title: changes to use zombie-bite
doc:
- audience: Node Operator
  description: |-
    In order to use [zombie-bite](https://github.com/paritytech/zombie-bite) (to fork and spawn a live network with the current _state_) with the same client binaries (for testing releases), we need to allow to set this value `DISPUTE_CANDIDATE_LIFETIME_AFTER_FINALIZATION` to __1__.

    Thx!
crates:
- name: polkadot-node-core-dispute-coordinator
  bump: patch
- name: polkadot-node-primitives
  bump: patch
